videos.headline: Wolf leaves game with leg injury
videos.description: Eli Wolf makes the catch and gets tackled. Wolf walks off the field with an injury.

videos.headline: Fils-aime trucks his way into the end zone
videos.description: Carlin Fils-aime extends the Volunteer lead with a 4-yard TD run.

videos.headline: Fils-aime finds the endzone once more
videos.description: Carlin Fils-aime breaks through the defense for a 30-yard TD run.

videos.headline: Johnson adds to Tennessee's lead before halftime
videos.description: Brandon Johnson escapes the cornerback for a 19-yard TD reception.

videos.headline: McClendon gets Indiana State on the board
videos.description: Jacquet McClendon scores on a 23-yard TD reception for the Sycamores.

videos.headline: Dormady picked off by Green in red zone
videos.description: Rondell Green intercepts a pass in the endzone for Indiana State.

videos.headline: Callaway breaks away from secondary for a TD
videos.description: Marquez Callaway gets by three defenders for for 37-yard TD

videos.headline: George TD reception caps it off for Vols
videos.description: Jeff George adds on for Tennessee late in 4th with a 11 yard TD catch.

videos.headline: Jones happy with team's performance after win
videos.description: Butch Jones discusses Tennessee's 42-7 win over Indiana State.

videos.headline: Dormady breaks down win over Indiana State
videos.description: QB Quinten Dormady improves to 2-0 on the season as the Vols start SEC play next week.

videos.headline: Tennessee's offense impressive after win over Indiana State.
videos.description: Matt Stinchcomb highlights the execution of the Volunteers after 42-7 win over Indiana State.

videos.headline: Tennessee cruises past Indiana State
videos.description: Quinten Dormady throws for 194 yards and two touchdowns as the No. 25 Volunteers beat the Sycamores 42-7.
